Product Description

Bath Toy Organizer, SUNDOKI Toy Holder Storage Bags with 4 Suction Cup Hooks and 2 Bath Toy Nets for Kids, Toddlers and Adults (Orange)

NEW VERSION--SUNDOKI Bath Toy Organizer Makes It Easier to Keep Your Toddlers’ Bath Toys Cleaned up

The enlarged extra storage space can hold more toys in one place and keep your kids’ bath toys from sitting in the bathtub

The 4 suction cup hooks are so strongly absorptive that can stick to tub walls steadily and allow bath toys to drain! You do not need to be worried that the hooks will fall off or be out of shape. It can hold things with the max load of 11 lb. Every cup hook is well made, thus it is easy to install or disassemble. What’s more，the surface of cup hook is so smooth that it will not hurt your hands when application and daily use

Designed with wider frame and strong stitching, the bath toy holders are durable to use season after season. Coming with 2 bath toy bags, one of the bags has 3 pockets to store soap, shampoo, toothpaste and all your other essentials.

Please be noted:

1. Do not install the suction cup hook near fire place;

2. Do not hang items over the max load (11LB) and fragile valuable items;

3. Toys in the pictures are not included;

4. Do not install hooks on the rugged surface: like soil walls, plaster surface or water-based coating surface. Please stick it on smooth ceramic tile, mirror or glass.

Package includes:

2 x bath toy organizers

4 x suction cup hooks

1 x User Manual

5.0 out of 5 starsConvenient and affordable.
January 20, 2019
Color: OrangeVerified Purchase
They were shipped out in a timely fashion. Once I received these I hung them up. That evening they did fall down. So the next day I put them back up but first I wetted the suction cups and have not had any other issues of them falling down. My kids, ages 5, 3, and 2 have taken baths in the tub since and have loved being able to get their toys of their choice while in the tub. There are even pockets on one of these that will hold the soap and shampoo. Also with them being made of mesh the water drains right out keeping the toys from getting all slimy and yucky. I would recommend these to anyone with young children. I would also suggest these for anyone who loves taking long hot baths. These will hold your bath salts, bath bombs, and anything else you may need for a long relaxing bath.

5.0 out of 5 starsAwesome bathroom toy organizer.
September 5, 2018
Color: OrangeVerified Purchase
I am extremely pleased with this bathroom toy organizer. It is excellent quality, easy to install and my kiddos love it. Compared to similar items like this one that I've purchased in the past, this one outshines everyone.

The netting and stitching on this organizer is very sturdy and is holding up pretty well to my kids and my constant abuse during bath time. The suction cups are nice and large and hold very fast to our bathroom wall (a bath fitter wall) and they seem to seal out moisture, so they are not getting that nasty mildew gunk underneath and falling off the wall. The compartments are large and can hold quite a bit and the suction cups are still holding fast with weight bearing on them. This organizer also seems to dry out fairly quickly and I have yet needed to wash it.

Definitely a bath/toy organizer that I recommend.
